ner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6e7de0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d6e7de0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Quem trabalha com a Shanghai Npack?\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2052fe8 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"2052fe8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-01f4660 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"01f4660\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>13+ anos atuando globalmente, Shanghai Npack exporta para 100+ pa\u00edses e atende 1,000+ clientes. 2012-2015: concentra\u00e7\u00e3o em \u00c1frica, M\u00e9dio Oriente e Sul da \u00c1sia. 2016-2025: expans\u00e3o para Europa, Am\u00e9ricas e Oceania nas ind\u00fastrias qu\u00edmica, cosm\u00e9tica, alimentar e farmac\u00eautica. Clientes incluem multinacionais e l\u00edderes chineses, comprovando nossa qualidade. Facilitamos visitas a f\u00e1bricas com nossos equipamentos para verifica\u00e7\u00e3o de desempenho. Npack \u00e9 o parceiro ideal para solu\u00e7\u00f5es de envase.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f276830 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f276830\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-89ab7f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"89ab7f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"wid